metadata.description:
BOY inside Image by Stacy Igel: "Sweet Home Chicago"
GIRL inside Image by Ami Ankin: "Mind Over Manhattan"

30% of BOY MEETS GIRL® net proceeds from this NFT sale will be donated to the Chicago Abortion Fund.

Original collector of this NFT can claim one custom BOY MEETS GIRL® hoodie designed with the artwork. One claim only, not applicable to secondary sales. Email contact@boymeetsgirlusa.com to claim.
